August 15, 2020 | https://matthewrayfield.com/articles/animating-urls-with-javascript-and-emojis/ | <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/*/https://matthewrayfield.com/articles/animating-urls-with-javascript-and-emojis/">archive.org</a>
